Pre-Depends: dpkg (>= 1.16.1), python3 (>= 3.11), ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, wlanpi-core
Description: WlanPi MCP Server
 wlanpi-mcp provides a Model Context Protocol (MCP) server that exposes
 WlanPi capabilities to AI assistants and MCP-compatible clients.
 .
 Supports both stdio transport (for direct Claude Desktop integration via SSH)
 and SSE/HTTP transport (for LAN-accessible daemon mode).
